mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Flashes from Detroit", "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Which Way Do I Face? (Style Series)", "Ladies on the Square: Accent on Elegance", "Dancer's Walkthru", "Tips for Dancers", "On the Record and the Record Report", "Equivalent Square Dance Movement", "Americana: Streets of Laredo", "Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Jack Jackson", "Paging the Roundancers: Grace Wolff", and "Experimental Lab: Substitute".
